for order flow
when a customer makes an order , the seller has to bring the order to the pickup station,
once the seller brings the goods , the admin will confirm that order has item delivered.



once the admin has confirmed that all items for a particular customer is complete , the admin wil confirm
the order which the dispatchs will now see on their app. 

once the dispatch accept any order , ther order will be on their list as order that needs to be delivered 
when the dispatch pickup the order to the user , and the user gives the dispatch ordercode , the dispatch 
can confirm that the order is delivered.

